        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI am not saying that this must be the final version, but it is the quickest way how to resolve name into ip and dont introduce another dependency - ping seems to be everywhere. This is just proof-of-concept for our discussion here: https://jira.onap.org/browse/OOM-1573",
